<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Car Management Project</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/dashboard.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            color: #333;
        }

        .about {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2em;
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1em;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #555;
        }

        ul {
            list-style-type: disc;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        ul li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 1em;
            color: #444;
            position: relative;
        }

        ul li::before {
            content: "âœ”";
            color: #2a9d8f;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 10px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }

        /* Responsive adjustments */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .about {
                margin: 20px;
                padding: 15px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 1.8em;
            }

            p, ul li {
                font-size: 0.95em;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header', { email: email }) %>

    <main>
        <section class="about">
            <h1>About the Car Management Project</h1>
            <p>Welcome to the Car Management Project! This project is designed to streamline and simplify the process of managing cars, whether for individual use or for a car rental or dealership business. Key features include vehicle tracking, maintenance scheduling, and easy access to essential car details.</p>
            <p>The Car Management Project enables users to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Register and manage cars in a centralized system</li>
                <li>Track car maintenance and service history</li>
                <li>Organize and categorize cars by model, year, and condition</li>
                <li>Monitor usage and availability for businesses</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Our goal is to make car management easy, efficient, and accessible. Thank you for choosing the Car Management Project to handle your automotive needs!</p>
        </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
